<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n10099d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n10" href="#n10099d">N10 (VI.B.16)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n10all.htm#n10099d"> 99(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> invest some security</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> All subscribers to the above appeal will enjoy the Blessing of Our Holy Father Pope Pius XI., and share in 10,000 Masses annually. Do not refuse to <mark>invest some security</mark> in this Treasury of God&apos;s Infinite Love, he will repay you here and in Eternity. <small> <a name="FJ1may24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#FJ1may24"><cite title="source">Freeman's Journal</cite></a> (1 May 1924) 4/1</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
